  "text": "Steam-flaking increases starch digestibility in the rumen and the total starch digested by cattle [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . It has been suggested that much of the increase in ruminal starch digestibility by steam-flaking is owing to changes in granular structure of starch, which causes additive effects beyond those of decreasing particle size [CITATION_3] .",
